    <div class="location">
      <h2>Buenos Aires</h2>
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200?text=Buenos+Aires" alt="Buenos Aires">
      <p>Buenos Aires is a captivating city known for its vibrant tango culture, elegant architecture, and delicious cuisine. Explore the historic neighborhoods, visit world-class museums, and enjoy the city's nightlife.</p>
      <button onclick="toggleInfo('buenosAires')">More Info</button>
      <div id="buenosAires" class="more-info">
